<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입 성공</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .success-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center; /* 가운데 정렬 */
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px; /* 최대 너비 설정 */
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #28a745; /* 성공 시 색상 */
            border: none;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #218838; /* 버튼 hover 시 색상 */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="success-container">
    <h2>회원가입이 성공하였습니다!</h2>
    <p>로그인 화면으로 이동합니다.</p>
    <button onclick="location.href='/login'">로그인 하기</button>
</div>

</body>
</html>